~The world is flat.~

-- ds.rendered.output:

-- ds.markdown:

~The world is flat.~

-- end: ds.rendered.output

-- end: ds.rendered


-- ds.markdown:

To create a superscript, use one caret symbol (^) before and after the 
characters.

-- ds.rendered: Superscript

-- ds.rendered.input:

\-- ds.markdown:

X^2^

-- ds.rendered.output:

-- ds.markdown:

X^2^

-- end: ds.rendered.output

-- end: ds.rendered


